snippet.title: Christopher Melcher
snippet.description:
#theLaw Live with Christopher C. Melcher covers legal issues, simply and insightfully. 

Host Christopher C. Melcher is one of the top divorce attorneys in California attorney, having represented clients in high-stakes litigation, from A-list celebrities to those with no means to pay. Chris's passion is helping others and making the law accessible to everyone. His father was a former prosecutor, who taught him how to be a lawyer, and what it means to be a lawyer.
